#description HearthKeep Bed Mat - STM32L476RG + 8× FSR-402
#
# Bed mat schematic for HearthKeep elder safety system.
# Components:
# - STM32L476RG (ultra-low-power Cortex-M4, 12-bit ADC)
# - 8× FSR-402 (Interlink force-sensitive resistors)
# - 8× HX711 (24-bit load cell amplifiers)
# - CD74HC4067 (16:1 multiplexer)
# - DS18B20 (waterproof temperature sensor)
# - SX1261 (868MHz LoRa radio)
# - MCP73831 (battery charger)
# - AP2112-3.3V regulators
# - LiPo 2000mAh battery + USB-C charging
# - Flexible PCB strip 800×60mm
#
# This is a placeholder - full KiCad schematic to be created.
#End